Voyager New Moves

Electric Terrain

Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
10 0 Electrifies the ground for 5 turns. Prevents sleep.

In the Field

If a Pokemon in your party knows or can learn Electric Terrain, then you can activate it to help you locate hidden items in the overworld.
When you deploy Electric Terrain, the Pokemon that used it will lose PP if it currently knows the move, or will lose HP if it does not.
When you find the hidden item or lose the signal, the terrain effect is removed.
You can unlock the ability to use Electric Terrain by participating in the "Transposing Trainer" side quest. The friendly illusionist Rarai will show you the technique after you battle her for the second time. Check the walkthrough for details!
